 $1 billion in assets -- spurring wild price moves while disconnecting thei=
r market values from underlying assets.=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0=
;">In the case of VXX, which allows traders to wager on gyrations in stock =
prices, the market fallout is potentially significant, with Goldman Sachs G=
roup Inc. strategists among those noting its size and influence among short=
